Raw mystery meat can be bought from the Darkmeyer Meat Shop for 1gp. It gives 30 Cooking XP when cooked into cooked mystery meat.

The raw mystery meat can be given to Frank, the little Bloodveld roaming Darkmeyer. Doing so gives the message "You let the bloodveld eat the mystery meat. He seems to enjoy it quite a lot."

Based on the examine text, it is likely that mystery meat is in fact human meat.
